sub_title: Medical Office Administrator at Valence Medical Imaging
summary:
Hard-working, efficient, and an excellent problem solver. I work well in groups as well as on my own, also exceptional organizational and time management skills.

I have extensive experience in customer service and providing a wonderful guest experience. I Excel in anticipating the needs and wants of others, and providing them with exceeded expectations. 

Skilled in Microsoft Office, Medical Transcription, and Medical Terminology. Certified in CPR, first aid, and the sterilization process using an Autoclave. Very open to learning new things and taking on all types of challenges.
